###
# Get book by id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books/1

###
# Get pageble books
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books?page=0&size=15&sortBy=createdDate&sortDir=desc

###
# Get pageble books
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books?page=1&size=5&sortBy=title&sortDir=asc

###
# Get pageble books
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books?page=&size=15&sortBy=authorName&sortDir=asc


